27567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-26T15:44:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>女友腳板底成日超大汗<br />\n有時開行冷氣一冚被對腳板底就會出哂汗<br />\n出完街佢對腳就會勁臭<br />\n但我平日就算著襪出街成日都唔會出汗<br />\n其實係我腳板底唔出汗唔正常定佢有問題</blockquote><br />\n著d透氣好d既鞋，著對厚d既襪索汗冇咁臭</blockquote><br />\n佢出得好誇張 只有唔著任何野先幫到佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"672cc5def6eacf79dceb05069275266643784562","tid":414924,"uid":27567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-26T15:45:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>會唔會係腳氣病啊</blockquote><br />\n腳氣病係會成日腳板出汗?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6eee374083b478f526557d51102fdce3096c10f9","tid":414924,"uid":27567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-26T15:46:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我手掌同腳板底長期出汗 嚴重時可以好似洗左手咁滴水</blockquote><br />\n原來好多人都係會腳板底出汗<br />\nbtw巴打咁多汗有咩辦法搞搞"},{"pid":"f83ef6ef29ad03ff76e8653e3c5907a457e67ad0","tid":414924,"uid":27567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-26T15:47:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>腳臭可能係雞眼/癬<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/36.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n又好似無 望落都白滑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a199c0f575db66e5d7eb9a89c59571ae0936b9c","tid":414924,"uid":52477,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-26T15:54:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>exactly the same<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n係你定你女友都係咁?<br />\n佢明明唔熱 腳板底都會出汗</blockquote><br />\n我呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n係架 唔熱架 手同腳出水出到仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf6cc8cb73cfe65d2307cfaaf49dad679a648131","tid":414924,"uid":60344,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-26T16:00:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>女友腳板底成日超大汗<br />\n有時開行冷氣一冚被對腳板底就會出哂汗<br />\n出完街佢對腳就會勁臭<br />\n但我平日就算著襪出街成日都唔會出汗<br />\n其實係我腳板底唔出汗唔正常定佢有問題</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔知咩事呢排好多汗<br />\n有芝士發酵味，好撚臭"},{"pid":"62765724568fc970203ee74c3a11a5d9d44b3d8b","tid":414924,"uid":58699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-26T16:01:45.000Z","msg":"影隻腳上黎睇睇 冇圖點知發生咩事 點樣幫到你"},{"pid":"8b7745684a6acffdf21ecb894e56cab2411da65f","tid":414924,"uid":79000,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-26T16:02:51.000Z","msg":"佢其他地方冇咩點出汗，<br />\n係手腳特別多<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/20.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n係真係好多果隻，同佢拖完手好似洗手咁"},{"pid":"ecd860888f262bbd1e9b4df15bd3015e80fd647c","tid":414924,"uid":60487,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-26T16:17:12.000Z","msg":"呢個係手汗腳汗問題<br />\n有時一緊張就會特別多<br />\n唔係啲汗臭,係汗+細菌臭<br />\n當有臭味時洗一洗走佢<br />\n<br />\n我試過真心有用嘅方法係<br />\n完全戒凍飲,以及每日都要早訓(12點前要訓)<br />\n持續一星期就開始見效<br />\n但係只要一飲凍野就會破功<br />\n(雖然好好好好好難做到,仲難過戒J)<br />\n<br />\n呢樣野係天生,唔好諗住做手術切斷交感神經<br />\n因為會有代償性多汗,出係其他地方<br />\n所以注重多D個人衛生洗多啲手同腳就算啦"},{"pid":"0995c65ebe78b8683390611fcd54863b9833c09f","tid":414924,"uid":61786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-26T16:59:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>會唔會係腳氣病啊</blockquote><br />\n腳氣病係會成日腳板出汗?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n如果冇損冇爛，咁就應該係汗腳。女朋友冬天隻腳板會唔會好易凍，一凍就凍到好似死屍咁？"}]}